<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<title>LEWORD 업데이트</title>
<HTA:APPLICATION
  APPLICATIONNAME="LEWORD Update"
  SCROLL="no"
  SINGLEINSTANCE="yes"
  BORDER="none"
  BORDERSTYLE="static"
  CAPTION="no"
  SHOWINTASKBAR="no"
  INNERBORDER="no"
  MAXIMIZEBUTTON="no"
  MINIMIZEBUTTON="no"
  SYSMENU="no"
  WINDOWSTATE="normal"
/>
<style>
  html, body { margin:0; padding:0; background:#0f0f23; color:#fff; font-family:'Malgun Gothic','맑은 고딕',sans-serif; overflow:hidden; height:100%; }
  .wrap { width:100%; height:100%; display:table; }
  .inner { display:table-cell; vertical-align:middle; text-align:center; padding:20px; }
  .title { font-size:18px; font-weight:bold; color:#fbbf24; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .version { font-size:12px; color:#8b8ba0; margin-bottom:24px; }
  .dot-wrap { margin: 0 auto 20px; height: 40px; }
  .dot { display:inline-block; width:12px; height:12px; margin:0 5px; background:#fbbf24; border-radius:50%; animation:bounce 1.4s infinite ease-in-out; }
  .dot:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: -0.32s; }
  .dot:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: -0.16s; }
  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 80%, 100% { transform: scale(0.5); opacity: 0.4; }
    40% { transform: scale(1.2); opacity: 1; }
  }
  .status { font-size:14px; color:#dadae6; font-weight:bold; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .sub { font-size:11px; color:#7c7c92; line-height:1.5; }
</style>
<script>
  window.resizeTo(420, 280);
  window.moveTo((screen.availWidth - 420) / 2, (screen.availHeight - 280) / 2);
  // 안전장치: 10분 후 자동 닫힘 (새 LEWORD splash가 taskkill 로 강제 종료 담당)
  setTimeout(function() { try { window.close(); } catch(e) {} }, 600000);
</script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="title">LEWORD 업데이트</div>
      <div class="version">설치 진행 중</div>
      <div class="dot-wrap">
        <span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="status">새 버전 설치 중...</div>
      <div class="sub">잠시 후 LEWORD가 자동으로 시작됩니다 (10~20초)</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
